item.title: What's New In RS Autoing?
item.dc:creator: @bloodrayne bloodrayne
item.description:
@bloodrayne wrote:

[quote=“Flat Line, post:1, topic:440043”]Hey all, its been a LONG time since I have played and I was thinking about autoing again. Are there new bots around? Any ones to avoid?

Also: I remember they had an update where you cant trade stuff for free, is that still around?[/quote]

For the moment, and most of the near future, I would avoid most java bots in general as they all seem to be a bit shady… People claim they’ve been hacked after using them, stuff like that. Simba/Scar is still around and working as it always has

Free trade is gone now and you can trade freely, except on new accounts, they’ll have limits until made members
